c: 57
v: 13
t: "On that day the hypocrites, both men and women, shall say to those who believe, \"Tarry for us, that we may kindle our light at yours.\" It shall be said, \"Return ye back, and seek light for yourselves.\" But between them shall be set a wall with a gateway, within which shall be the Mercy, and in front, without it, the Torment"